author: Xbox
description:
Play the Demo and prepare to embark in a quest to bring back the White Birds in Amerzone – The Explorer’s Legacy, available on Xbox Series X|S on April 24th.

Answer the call of exploration as you travel to the Amerzone, a forgotten Latin American country, to fulfill the last wishes of a late explorer. Investigate the ruins of this secretive land reclaimed by nature, meet intriguing characters with deep backstories and solve intricate puzzles to unveil the truth.
